data.description: Presenting 2109 Pepperell Drive – Your new haven of comfort and freedom! This charming 3-bedroom home, with an additional office, boasts an open, split floor plan across 1988 sq ft.  Large, open living room with wood burning fireplace. The kitchen is updated with stainless steel appliances, ready to inspire your inner chef. The 2 full bathrooms ensure convenience and privacy. The rear porch is spacious and screened in for year-round enjoyment.  Recent upgrades include a new HVAC system, roof, and exterior and interior paint – all done in 2021.  Situated on a sprawling 1.39-acre lot, this property comes with no deed restrictions or HOA, offering plenty of space for your toys, boats, RV, and more! The septic tank was serviced in 2021, providing additional peace of mind.  Conveniently located close to beaches, the airport, and plenty of shopping!  Zoned for top rated schools! Make your appointment today before it's too late!
